Lukas Haas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lukas_Haas 0 Lukas Daniel Haas (born April 16, 1976) is an American actor and musician. His acting career has spanned three decades, during which he has appeared in more than 50 feature films and a number of television shows and stage productions.
